<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Subscription Activated</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #0f1117;
      color: #e8e8e8;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .card {
      background: #1a1d27;
      border: 1px solid #2a2d3a;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 48px 40px;
      max-width: 520px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    h1 {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #a0a3b1;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .notice {
      background: #1e2235;
      border: 1px solid #3a3d55;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      margin: 28px 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .notice strong {
      color: #f0c040;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .notice p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #c0c3d1;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #229ed9;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 8px;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .btn:hover { background: #1a8bbf; }
    .small {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #606370;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">✅</div>
    <h1>Payment Successful!</h1>
    <p>Thank you for subscribing. You should receive a message from our Telegram bot shortly with your channel invite link.</p>

    <div class="notice">
      <strong>⚠️ Is your Telegram account set to private?</strong>
      <p>If your Telegram privacy settings prevent messages from unknown contacts, our bot won't be able to reach you automatically. Click the button below to activate your access manually — it only takes a second.</p>
    </div>

    <a class="btn" href="https://t.me/EdgeScoutAdminBot?start=activate" target="_blank">
      Activate Access on Telegram
    </a>

    <p class="small">Only needed if your Telegram is set to private. Public accounts will receive the invite link automatically.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
